{"prompt": "Design an engaging platform for a podcast network. The aesthetic should incorporate a bold magenta.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Podcast Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #333333;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff00ff, #e000e0);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .podcast-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n        .podcast-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .podcast-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .podcast-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #ff00ff;\n        }\n        .podcast-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .cta-section {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n        }\n        .cta-section h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #ff00ff;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: #ff00ff;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e000e0;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>PodVerse Network</h1>\n            <p>Tune into the stories that matter.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"podcast-list\">\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ff00ff/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 1\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>The Daily Grind</h3>\n                    <p>A deep dive into the everyday lives of extraordinary people. Inspiring stories and practical advice.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e000e0/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 2\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>Tech Unpacked</h3>\n                    <p>Demystifying the latest in technology. From AI to cybersecurity, we break it down for you.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/cc00cc/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 3\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>Mindful Moments</h3>\n                    <p>Your weekly dose of calm. Explore mindfulness, meditation, and mental well-being with expert insights.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/aa00aa/ffffff?text=Podcast+4\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 4\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-info\">\n                    <h3>Global Pulse</h3>\n                    <p>Understanding the world we live in. Current events, geopolitical analysis, and diverse perspectives.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"cta-section\">\n            <h2>Discover Your Next Favorite Podcast</h2>\n            <p>Explore our full catalog and subscribe today!</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Browse All Podcasts</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 PodVerse Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JS for potential future interactivity\n        document.querySelectorAll('.podcast-item').forEach(item => {\n            item.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                // In a real app, this would navigate to a podcast detail page\n                alert('You clicked on a podcast! Learn more coming soon.');\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}